snippet.textDisplay: Is the reason we're getting the other characters in 4 month intervals instead of 3 because you haven't started working on them? I know with the last fighter pass, just like with the Wii/3DS dlc, you already had characters in the middle of being made. I'm just wondering because 2 years to get 6 characters is long, a lot of casual players might not be interested in the game by the end of this year let alone by the end of 2021. You could have echo fighters being brought in, I already think that term isn't being utilized despite being made for characters in this game. Sandman for little mac, Dr Eggman being an echo of Bowser Jr, Metal Sonic being a Sonic echo, Miss Pacman, Ring fit Trainer, I don't like Dixie Kong but I know a lot of people want her, Dr Luigi, just something to keep fans invested in the game. You could double the amount of mii fighters and stage creators we could make, I already ran out months ago and am forcing myself to delete some to make room for more. I don't want to sound greedy or rude, especially after how much Sakurai has done for us, we could never know how hard it is to make this game and these characters, so thank you for all you have done Sakurai.
snippet.textOriginal: Is the reason we're getting the other characters in 4 month intervals instead of 3 because you haven't started working on them? I'm just wondering because 2 years to get 6 characters is long, a lot of casual players might not be interested in the game by the end of this year let alone by the end of 2021. You could have echo fighters being brought in, I already think that term isn't being utilized despite being made for characters in this game. Sandman for little mac, Dr Eggman being an echo of Bowser Jr, Metal Sonic being a Sonic echo, Miss Pacman, Ring fit Trainer, I don't like Dixie Kong but I know a lot of people want her, Dr Luigi, just something to keep fans invested in the game. You could double the amount of mii fighters and stage creators we could make, I already ran out months ago and am forcing myself to delete some to make room for more. I don't want to sound greedy or rude, especially after how much Sakurai has done for us, we could never know how hard it is to make this game and these characters, so thank you for all you have done Sakurai.
